{"tid":301570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【與百億太子爺戀情曝光】34歲阿Sa 最新回應：依家好開心","createTime":"2017-06-28T17:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T08:07:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9b08ef719b630321aec9c0ceabe0dc40c5dcd8","tid":301570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:54:42.000Z","msg":"2017年06月28日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498619553_dedc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498619553_dedc.jpg&h=6b9eb32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n34歲蔡卓妍(Sa)自從同鄭中基離婚、2015年又同「的士陳」分手，阿Sa感情dry足咁耐，全程投入工作，不過今日有周刊指，阿Sa多得好友何超蓮同馬天佑撥「大葵扇」，阿Sa同「麻將館大王」太子爺石恆聰（Anthony）今年4月拍拖，個名好熟，之唔係連詩雅舊愛囉!<br />\n<br />\n阿Sa透過短訊回應《蘋果》稱：「o依家好開心，多謝大家關心，其他唔講咁多了!」<br />\n據周刊指，阿Sa上周日更被影到兩度上男友位於畢架山嘅屋企過夜，阿Sa七人車直駛入大宅，之後阿Sa先落車，據周刊指，連詩雅同Anthony喺2014年撻着，上年宣佈分訊，但12月秘密翻撻，今年2月又再分手，三年間離離合合，盛傳係Anthony覺得連詩雅未玩夠先決定分開，不過連詩雅一直想復合，知道阿Sa同Anthony一齊，佢都冇放棄，但係石母比較喜歡阿Sa，覺得阿Sa有本事搵銀，而唔係貪阿仔啲錢。<br />\n周刊又指，阿Sa去過夜嗰間市值3.3億嘅大宅，係石家今年3月先買，由Anthony四兄弟姊妹持有。Anthony係城中鑽石筍盤，為「麻將大王」石鑑輝後人，石鑑輝當年係四大華探長呂樂身邊嘅紅人，除咗開麻雀館，仲有不少物業，估計市值逾百億。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170628/56885698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170628%2F56885698&d=jzoBtcDn5a4I92ZefLOOqQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=be9f36b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170628%2F56885698&h=d4a6c94a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170628/56885698</a>"},{"pid":"45b3c82fcfb362f47325a454a1055c2420013507","tid":301570,"uid":38102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:22:39.000Z","msg":"口味一致<br />\n都係細胸長腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402fceffe892af7c363d3c345ecd7b51914c0842","tid":301570,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:48:42.000Z","msg":"呢條仔個背景好黑吓喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb4a84ecec74e99cbdd775a592c05ef7ff332d4","tid":301570,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"盛傳係Anthony覺得連詩雅未玩夠先決定分開，不過連詩雅一直想復合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cba5b2101a5c3d15e31980f9b39899f2dc5b4be","tid":301570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89177ba634f22859e6149e8a05dfc62f1a844cb","tid":301570,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2088aaf5505176f5f85a494fd15fbfec17df202","tid":301570,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"扑左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4604715958ade603b24023517d8042df45b27ba","tid":301570,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"黑底"}]}